Controls where PKI and encryption keys will be generated, and, when securely
copied to Nodes during bootstrapping, where it will be sourced from.

Examples:
  # See how this value affects PKI generation.
  KWM_CONFIG_PATH_LOCAL=test $SCRIPT_NAME render pki

  # See how this value affects copying PKI.
  KWM_CONFIG_PATH_LOCAL=test $SCRIPT_NAME render etcd-node <nodeKey> | head -n 10
